@stefanbar put it on live after i asked him to put it on live.

The reason for it going to live is because the setup installs/downloads the latest version from the website (there is only a live website). The application needs to be installed to be integrated with windows.

It has always been on live. Yes we know that we should not put things to live as it might have bugs, but since the previous version that was on live already completely never worked. This solved that as well.

